data.text:
Mishti is an Indian actress and model

Image Credit: Instagram / mishtichakravarty

She primarily works in the Telugu, Hindi, Bengali, and Kannada film industries.

Image Credit: Instagram / mishtichakravarty

She was born on December 20, 1987, in Kolkata, West Bengal, India.

Image Credit: Instagram / mishtichakravarty

Mishti made her acting debut with the Telugu film "Chinnadana Nee Kosam" in 2014.

Image Credit: Instagram / mishtichakravarty

She gained recognition for her performance in the Bollywood film "Kaanchi: The Unbreakable,"

Image Credit: Instagram / mishtichakravarty
